sites and applications right from GitHub. The Netlify platform connects your repositories to an all-in-one workflow for global CDN deployment, continuous integration, and automatic (and free) HTTPS. Each time you commit changes, Netlify builds your site, prerenders markup, and optimizes assets on dedicated build infrastructure. Easily create an entirely automated workflows for your web applications\r\n\r\n## Features\r\n\r\n### Push your site live, directly from GitHub\r\nDeploy your site to an ultra-redundant global CDN that’s purpose built for serving pages and assets quickly and consistently.\r\n\r\n### Automate deployment\r\nNetlify’s built-in Continuous Deployment automatically runs your build commands and deploys the result whenever you push to your Git repository.\r\n\r\n### Add a custom domain\r\nPurchase domains and manage DNS zones and records right inside of Netlify.\r\n\r\n### HTTPS is automatic\r\nYour site will automatically be secured with a free TLS certificate from Let’s Encrypt.\r\n\r\n### Deploy Previews\r\nNetlify’s Deploy Previews streamlined your workflow by giving you a unique, permanent URL to check what your changes will be like in production whenever you submit a pull request.\r\n\r\n### And a lot more!\r\nNetlify includes solutions for forms, identity, and even custom functions powered by AWS Lambda. And all this functionality can be configured directly in your repo.\r\n","external_url":"https://www.netlify.com","html_url":"https://github.com/apps/netlify","created_at":"2018-06-12T15:16:51Z","updated_at":"2025-07-17T12:19:42Z","permissions":{"checks":"write","contents":"read","emails":"read","issues":"write","metadata":"read","pull_requests":"write","statuses":"write"},"events":["create","delete","issue_comment","pull_request","pull_request_review","pull_request_review_comment","push"]},"minimized":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/comments/4625270282","html_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/4533#issuecomment-4625270282","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/4533","id":4625270282,"node_id":"IC_kwDOLW-eZs8AAAABE7AGCg","user":{"login":"aarongarciah","id":7225802,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMjU4MDI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7225802?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah","html_url":"https://github.com/aarongarciah","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2026-06-04T19:06:10Z","updated_at":"2026-06-04T19:06:10Z","body":"Hey @Jihye2ee, thanks for the PR. Unfortunately, we won't be moving forward with it. Toasts are used to notify users without interrupting their workflow, and moving the focus to a toast is not desired.\r\n\r\nIn scenarios when users' input is required, [AlertDialog](https://base-ui.com/react/components/alert-dialog) is better suited.\r\n\r\nA toast is close to the Alert pattern from the [APG guidelines](https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/alert/):\r\n\r\n> Because alerts are intended to provide important and potentially time-sensitive information without interfering with the user's ability to continue working, _it is crucial they do not affect keyboard focus_. The [Alert Dialog Pattern](https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/alertdialog/) is designed for situations where interrupting work flow is necessary.\r\n\r\n","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/comments/4625270282/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"minimized":null}]